data_container = ListDataContainer(current_ids=[str(i) for i in range(100)],
    data_inputs=np.array(list(range(100))), expected_outputs=np.array(list(
    range(100, 200))))
data_container.concat(DataContainer(current_ids=[str(i) for i in range(100,
    200)], data_inputs=np.array(list(range(100, 200))), expected_outputs=np
    .array(list(range(200, 300)))))
assert np.array_equal(np.array(data_container.current_ids), np.array(list(
    range(0, 200))).astype(np.str))
expected_data_inputs = np.array(list(range(0, 200))).astype(np.int)
actual_data_inputs = np.array(data_container.data_inputs).astype(np.int)
assert np.array_equal(actual_data_inputs, expected_data_inputs)
expected_expected_outputs = np.array(list(range(100, 300))).astype(np.int)
assert np.array_equal(np.array(data_container.expected_outputs).astype(np.
    int), expected_expected_outputs)
